{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "bookName": "2 Nephi",
  "chapter": 31,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "iJpuSZDxZSBJHFSeavba",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "sister-m"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 109.913,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 0.5,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, make an end of my prophesying unto you,",
      "verse": "31:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 0.68,
      "end": 1.18,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my beloved brethren.",
      "verse": "31:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 1.36,
      "end": 1.86,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I cannot write but a few things,",
      "verse": "31:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 2.04,
      "end": 2.54,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I know must surely come to pass;",
      "verse": "31:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 2.72,
      "end": 3.22,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither can I write but a few of the words of my brother Jacob.",
      "verse": "31:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 3.9,
      "end": 4.4,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, the things which I have written sufficeth me,",
      "verse": "31:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 4.58,
      "end": 5.08,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save it be a few words which I must speak concerning the doctrine of Christ;",
      "verse": "31:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 5.26,
      "end": 5.76,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, I shall speak unto you plainly,",
      "verse": "31:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 5.94,
      "end": 6.44,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the plainness of my prophesying.",
      "verse": "31:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 7.12,
      "end": 7.62,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For my soul delighteth in plainness;",
      "verse": "31:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 7.8,
      "end": 8.3,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for after this manner doth the Lord God work among the children of men.",
      "verse": "31:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 8.48,
      "end": 8.98,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For the Lord God giveth light unto the understanding;",
      "verse": "31:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 9.16,
      "end": 9.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he speaketh unto men",
      "verse": "31:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 9.84,
      "end": 10.34,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to their language,",
      "verse": "31:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 10.52,
      "end": 11.02,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto their understanding.",
      "verse": "31:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 11.7,
      "end": 12.2,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I would that ye should remember",
      "verse": "31:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 12.38,
      "end": 12.88,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I have spoken unto you concerning that prophet",
      "verse": "31:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 13.06,
      "end": 13.56,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which the Lord showed unto me,",
      "verse": "31:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 13.74,
      "end": 14.24,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that should baptize the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "31:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 14.42,
      "end": 14.92,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which should take away the sins of the world.",
      "verse": "31:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 15.6,
      "end": 16.1,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, if the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "31:5",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 16.28,
      "end": 16.78,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he being holy,",
      "verse": "31:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 16.96,
      "end": 17.46,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should have need to be baptized by water,",
      "verse": "31:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 17.64,
      "end": 18.14,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to fulfil all righteousness,",
      "verse": "31:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 18.32,
      "end": 18.82,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O then, how much more need have we,",
      "verse": "31:5",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 19.0,
      "end": 19.5,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "being unholy,",
      "verse": "31:5",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 19.68,
      "end": 20.18,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to be baptized,",
      "verse": "31:5",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 20.36,
      "end": 20.86,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even by water!",
      "verse": "31:5",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 21.54,
      "end": 22.04,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, I would ask of you, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "31:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 22.22,
      "end": 22.72,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "how the Lamb of God did fulfil all righteousness",
      "verse": "31:6",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 22.9,
      "end": 23.4,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in being baptized by water?",
      "verse": "31:6",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 24.08,
      "end": 24.58,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Know ye not that he was holy?",
      "verse": "31:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 24.76,
      "end": 25.26,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But notwithstanding he being holy,",
      "verse": "31:7",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 25.44,
      "end": 25.94,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he showeth unto the children of men",
      "verse": "31:7",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 26.12,
      "end": 26.62,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that, according to the flesh",
      "verse": "31:7",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 26.8,
      "end": 27.3,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he humbleth himself before the Father,",
      "verse": "31:7",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 27.48,
      "end": 27.98,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and witnesseth unto the Father",
      "verse": "31:7",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 28.16,
      "end": 28.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he would be obedient unto him in keeping his commandments.",
      "verse": "31:7",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 29.34,
      "end": 29.84,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, after he was baptized with water",
      "verse": "31:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 30.02,
      "end": 30.52,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Holy Ghost descended upon him in the form of a dove.",
      "verse": "31:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 31.2,
      "end": 31.7,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And again, it showeth unto the children of men",
      "verse": "31:9",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 31.88,
      "end": 32.38,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the straitness of the path,",
      "verse": "31:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 32.56,
      "end": 33.06,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the narrowness of the gate,",
      "verse": "31:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 33.24,
      "end": 33.74,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by which they should enter,",
      "verse": "31:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 33.92,
      "end": 34.42,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he having set the example before them.",
      "verse": "31:9",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 35.1,
      "end": 35.6,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said unto the children of men:",
      "verse": "31:10",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 35.78,
      "end": 36.28,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Follow thou me.",
      "verse": "31:10",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 36.46,
      "end": 38.736,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "31:10",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 38.916,
      "end": 39.416,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "can we follow Jesus",
      "verse": "31:10",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 39.596,
      "end": 40.096,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save we shall be willing to keep the commandments of the Father?",
      "verse": "31:10",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 40.776,
      "end": 41.276,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Father said:",
      "verse": "31:11",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 41.456,
      "end": 41.956,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Repent ye, repent ye,",
      "verse": "31:11",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 42.136,
      "end": 42.636,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and be baptized in the name of my Beloved Son.",
      "verse": "31:11",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 43.316,
      "end": 43.816,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also, the voice of the Son came unto me, saying:",
      "verse": "31:12",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 43.996,
      "end": 44.496,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "He that is baptized in my name,",
      "verse": "31:12",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 44.676,
      "end": 45.176,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to him will the Father give the Holy Ghost,",
      "verse": "31:12",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 45.356,
      "end": 45.856,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "like unto me;",
      "verse": "31:12",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 46.036,
      "end": 46.536,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, follow me,",
      "verse": "31:12",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 46.716,
      "end": 47.216,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and do the things which ye have seen me do.",
      "verse": "31:12",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 47.896,
      "end": 50.172,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "31:13",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 50.352,
      "end": 50.852,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I know that if ye shall follow the Son,",
      "verse": "31:13",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 51.032,
      "end": 51.532,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with full purpose of heart,",
      "verse": "31:13",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 51.712,
      "end": 52.212,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "acting no hypocrisy and no deception before God,",
      "verse": "31:13",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 52.392,
      "end": 52.892,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but with real intent,",
      "verse": "31:13",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 53.072,
      "end": 53.572,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "repenting of your sins,",
      "verse": "31:13",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 53.752,
      "end": 54.252,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "witnessing unto the Father",
      "verse": "31:13",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 54.432,
      "end": 54.932,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye are willing to take upon you the name of Christ, by baptism\u2014",
      "verse": "31:13",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 55.112,
      "end": 55.612,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, by following your Lord and your Savior down into the water,",
      "verse": "31:13",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 55.792,
      "end": 56.292,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to his word,",
      "verse": "31:13",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 56.472,
      "end": 56.972,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, then shall ye receive the Holy Ghost;",
      "verse": "31:13",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 57.152,
      "end": 57.652,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, then cometh the baptism of fire and of the Holy Ghost;",
      "verse": "31:13",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 57.832,
      "end": 58.332,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and then can ye speak with the tongue of angels,",
      "verse": "31:13",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 58.512,
      "end": 59.012,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shout praises unto the Holy One of Israel.",
      "verse": "31:13",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 59.692,
      "end": 60.192,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But, behold, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "31:14",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 60.372,
      "end": 60.872,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "thus came the voice of the Son unto me, saying:",
      "verse": "31:14",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 61.052,
      "end": 61.552,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "After ye have repented of your sins,",
      "verse": "31:14",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 61.732,
      "end": 62.232,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and witnessed unto the Father",
      "verse": "31:14",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 62.412,
      "end": 62.912,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye are willing to keep my commandments,",
      "verse": "31:14",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 63.092,
      "end": 63.592,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by the baptism of water,",
      "verse": "31:14",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 63.772,
      "end": 64.272,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and have received the baptism of fire and of the Holy Ghost,",
      "verse": "31:14",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 64.452,
      "end": 64.952,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and can speak with a new tongue,",
      "verse": "31:14",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 65.132,
      "end": 65.632,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even with the tongue of angels,",
      "verse": "31:14",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 65.812,
      "end": 66.312,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after this should deny me,",
      "verse": "31:14",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 66.492,
      "end": 66.992,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it would have been better for you that ye had not known me.",
      "verse": "31:14",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 67.672,
      "end": 68.172,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I heard a voice from the Father, saying:",
      "verse": "31:15",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 68.352,
      "end": 68.852,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, the words of my Beloved are true and faithful.",
      "verse": "31:15",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 69.032,
      "end": 69.532,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "He that endureth to the end,",
      "verse": "31:15",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 69.712,
      "end": 70.212,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the same shall be saved.",
      "verse": "31:15",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 70.892,
      "end": 72.935,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "31:16",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 73.115,
      "end": 73.615,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I know by this",
      "verse": "31:16",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 73.795,
      "end": 74.295,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that unless a man shall endure to the end,",
      "verse": "31:16",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 74.475,
      "end": 74.975,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in following the example of the Son of the living God,",
      "verse": "31:16",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 75.155,
      "end": 75.655,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he cannot be saved.",
      "verse": "31:16",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 76.335,
      "end": 76.835,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, do the things",
      "verse": "31:17",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 77.015,
      "end": 77.515,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I have told you I have seen that your Lord and your Redeemer should do;",
      "verse": "31:17",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 77.695,
      "end": 78.195,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for, for this cause have they been shown unto me,",
      "verse": "31:17",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 78.375,
      "end": 78.875,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye might know the gate by which ye should enter.",
      "verse": "31:17",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 79.055,
      "end": 79.555,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For the gate by which ye should enter is repentance and baptism by water;",
      "verse": "31:17",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 79.735,
      "end": 80.235,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and then cometh a remission of your sins by fire and by the Holy Ghost.",
      "verse": "31:17",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 80.915,
      "end": 81.415,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then are ye in this strait and narrow path",
      "verse": "31:18",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 81.595,
      "end": 82.095,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which leads to eternal life;",
      "verse": "31:18",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 82.275,
      "end": 82.775,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, ye have entered in by the gate;",
      "verse": "31:18",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 82.955,
      "end": 83.455,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye have done according to the commandments of the Father and the Son;",
      "verse": "31:18",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 83.635,
      "end": 84.135,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and ye have received the Holy Ghost,",
      "verse": "31:18",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 84.315,
      "end": 84.815,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which witnesses of the Father and the Son,",
      "verse": "31:18",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 84.995,
      "end": 85.495,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the fulfilling of the promise which he hath made,",
      "verse": "31:18",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 85.675,
      "end": 86.175,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that if ye entered in by the way ye should receive.",
      "verse": "31:18",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 86.855,
      "end": 88.898,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "31:19",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 89.078,
      "end": 89.578,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after ye have gotten into this strait and narrow path,",
      "verse": "31:19",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 89.758,
      "end": 90.258,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I would ask if all is done?",
      "verse": "31:19",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 90.438,
      "end": 93.642,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I say unto you, Nay;",
      "verse": "31:19",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 93.822,
      "end": 94.322,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for ye have not come thus far",
      "verse": "31:19",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 94.502,
      "end": 95.002,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save it were by the word of Christ",
      "verse": "31:19",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 95.182,
      "end": 95.682,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with unshaken faith in him,",
      "verse": "31:19",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 95.862,
      "end": 96.362,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "relying wholly upon the merits of him who is mighty to save.",
      "verse": "31:19",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 97.042,
      "end": 97.542,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, ye must press forward with a steadfastness in Christ,",
      "verse": "31:20",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 97.722,
      "end": 98.222,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having a perfect brightness of hope,",
      "verse": "31:20",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 98.402,
      "end": 98.902,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and a love of God and of all men.",
      "verse": "31:20",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 99.082,
      "end": 99.582,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, if ye shall press forward,",
      "verse": "31:20",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 99.762,
      "end": 100.262,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "feasting upon the word of Christ,",
      "verse": "31:20",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 100.442,
      "end": 100.942,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and endure to the end,",
      "verse": "31:20",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 101.122,
      "end": 101.622,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, thus saith the Father:",
      "verse": "31:20",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 101.802,
      "end": 102.302,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Ye shall have eternal life.",
      "verse": "31:20",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 102.982,
      "end": 103.482,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, behold, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "31:21",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 103.662,
      "end": 104.162,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "this is the way;",
      "verse": "31:21",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 104.342,
      "end": 104.842,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there is none other way nor name given under heaven",
      "verse": "31:21",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 105.022,
      "end": 105.522,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whereby man can be saved in the kingdom of God.",
      "verse": "31:21",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 105.702,
      "end": 106.202,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, behold, this is the doctrine of Christ,",
      "verse": "31:21",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 106.382,
      "end": 106.882,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the only and true doctrine of the Father and of the Son,",
      "verse": "31:21",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 107.062,
      "end": 107.562,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and of the Holy Ghost,",
      "verse": "31:21",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 107.742,
      "end": 108.242,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is one God, without end.",
      "verse": "31:21",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 108.422,
      "end": 109.258,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "31:21",
      "lineIndex": 135
    }
  ]
}